snippet.title: Rune Factory 3 Special - Nintendo Direct 9.13.2022
snippet.description:
Rune Factory 3 Special is coming to Nintendo Switch next year! Wishlist today:  https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/rune-factory-3-special-switch/

Live your fantasy life as Micah, who can transform into two forms. Farm, fight and fall in love as you revisit a classic in the series that perfected the blend of RPG & Life-sim genres.

#RuneFactory3S #NintendoDirect #NintendoSwitch

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot

Visit Nintendo.com for all the latest! http://www.nintendo.com/
